verbose_text: However, the levels of p16 and p21 were decreased in the miR-20b inhibitor + siTXNIP group compared with those in the miR-20b inhibitor + NC group, and that the levels of p16 and p21 were lower in the miR-20b inhibitor + H 2 O 2 + siTXNIP group compared with those in miR-20b inhibitor + H 2 O 2 + NC group (P < 0.05; XREF_FIG).
